Titolo: Façade (video game)

Anno: 2005

Descrizione: Façade is an artificial-intelligence-based interactive story created by Michael Mateas and Andrew Stern. It was the winner of the Grand Jury Prize at the 2006 Slamdance Independent Games Festival and has been exhibited at several international art shows. In 2010, it was included as one of the titles in the book 1001 Video Games You Must Play Before You Die.

Genere: Interactive movie / Interactive drama 

Valutazione: N/A
